# Piano
# P, Exercises
--- piano-exercises
ExerciseMin251: [zipT(pickKeysShuf().flat(), s(`:`), ss(`3b5b7b1 713b5b`))] {maybeEvery(5, '')}
ExerciseMaj251: [zipLongest(pickKeys().flat(), s(`:`), ss(`32 7b5`))] {maybeEvery(3, '')}
ExerciseFlipflops: 35/34 [zipLongest(pickKeysShuf().flat(), s(`:`), ss(`57 34`))] {maybeEvery(`3,1`, '')}
ExerciseStepwiseDia: [zipLongest(pickKeysShuf().flat(), s(`:`), ss(`5 6 7 56 34 24`))] {maybeEvery(`4,1`, '')}
--- piano-second
BrahmsWiegelied: play
Scale-alt: play alt resolutions (678910 is flat)
HWLicks: pick three
PiaScale: G minor, [ss(`regular, russian, thirds, sixths, octaves`)], [ss(`I, Im, VIb, VIm, IV, IVm, I7, VIb7, IV7, II7, Idim7`)]
GluckAccomp: play
JazzFutter: [zipT(ss(`30 32 33 34 35 36 37`), s(`///////////`), pickKeysShuf().flat())]
ModernPianoPatterns: check out (1 barrons, 2 pustoņa triādes kvintās uz augšu pa 6)
# https://www.instagram.com/reel/DVI12O2iSwG/
AutumnLeaves: pick and play the voicings
TriSubs: play [pickKeys({split: 3, shuffle: true})]
